ComicInfo.Summary: Francine's outfit is a big hit with the director of a condom commercial and is thrust into the limelight. At home she is still having trouble coming to terms with her love of Katchoo and symbolically locks herself in a closet. Rachael and Chuck's relationship is put into more focus and a shocking truth is revealed. David confesses he is very religious and that Christianity has saved his life.
